(1277, 'ayrb', 'from (01254) (in the sense of (01262))', 'bariy\'', 'TWOT - 279a', 'baw-ree\'', 'Adjective', 'from «01254» (in the sense of «01262»); fatted or plump:--fat ((fleshed), -ter), fed, firm, plenteous, rank.', '<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>fat<LI>(TWOT) fat, fatter, fed, firm, plenteous, rank</OL>'),
