(1281, 'xyrb', 'from (01272)', 'bariyach', 'TWOT - 284a', 'baw-ree\'-akh', '', 'or (shortened) bariach {baw-ree\'-akh}; from «01272»; a fugitive, i.e. the serpent (as fleeing), and the constellation by that name:--crooked, noble, piercing.', 'adj<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>fleeing subst<LI>fugitive</OL>'),
