(1326, 'htb', 'probably an orthographical variation for (01327)', 'bathah', 'TWOT - 298c', 'baw-thaw\'', 'Noun Feminine', 'probably an orthographical variation for «01327»; desolation:--waste.', '<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>end, destruction</OL>'),
