(1614, 'tyrpg', 'probably from (01613)', 'gophriyth', 'TWOT - 375', 'gof-reeth\'', 'Noun Feminine', 'probably feminine of «01613»; properly, cypress- resin; by analogy, sulphur (as equally inflammable):--brimstone.', '<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>brimstone<OL TYPE=\"a\"><LI>of judgment (fig.)<LI>of Jehovah\'s breath (fig.)</OL></OL>'),
