(1616, 'rg', 'from (01481)', 'ger', 'TWOT - 330a', 'gare', 'Noun Masculine', 'or (fully) geyr (gare); from «01481»; properly, a guest; by implication, a foreigner:--alien, sojourner, stranger.', '<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>sojourner<OL TYPE=\"a\"><LI>a temporary inhabitant, a newcomer lacking inherited rights<LI>of foreigners in Israel, though conceded rights</OL></OL>'),
