(2216, 'lbbbrz', 'from (02215) and (0894)', 'Zrubbabel', 'TWOT - 578a', 'zer-oob-baw-bel\'', 'Proper Name Masculine', 'from «02215» and «0894»; descended of (i.e. from) Babylon, i.e. born there; Zerubbabel, an Israelite:--Zerubbabel.', 'Zerubbabel = \"sown in Babylon\"<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>the grandson of king Jehoiachin and leader of the first group of returning exiles from Babylon</OL>'),
