(2250, 'hrwbbx', 'from (02266)', 'chabbuwrah', 'TWOT - 598g', 'khab-boo-raw\'', 'Noun Feminine', 'or chabburah {khab-boo-raw\'}; or chaburah {khab-oo-raw\'}; from «02266»; properly, bound (with stripes), i.e. a weal (or black-and-blue mark itself):--blueness, bruise, hurt, stripe, wound.', '<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>bruise, stripe, wound, blow</OL>'),
