(2257, 'lbx', 'from (02255)', 'chabal', 'TWOT - 2716a', 'khab-al\'', 'Noun Masculine', '(Aramaic) from «02255»; harm (personal or pecuniary):--damage, hurt.', '<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>hurt, damage, injury</OL>'),
