(2262, 'hynccbx', 'of uncertain derivation', 'Chabatstsanyah', 'None', 'khab-ats-tsan-yaw\'', 'Proper Name Masculine', 'of uncertain derivation; Chabatstsanjah, a Rechabite:--Habazaniah.', 'Habaziniah = \"light of Jehovah\"<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>apparently the head of one of the families of the Rechabites</OL>'),
