(2996, 'hnby', 'from (01129)', 'Yabneh', 'None', 'yab-neh\'', 'Proper Name Location', 'from «01129»; a building; Jabneh, a place in Palestine:--Jabneh.', 'Jabneh = \"building of God\"<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>a Philistine city</OL>'),
