(3265, 'rw[y', 'apparently the passive participle of the same as (03293)', 'Ya`uwr', 'None', 'yaw-oor\'', 'Proper Name Masculine', 'apparently the passive participle of the same as «03293»; wooded; Jaur, an Israelite:--Jair(from the margin).', 'Jair = \"forested\"<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>father of Elhanan the giant slayer, one of David\'s mighty warriors<OL TYPE=\"a\"><LI>also called \'Jaare-oregim\'</OL></OL>'),
