(3270, 'ryz[y', 'from (05826)', 'Ya`azeyr', 'None', 'yah-az-ayr\'', 'Proper Name Location', 'or Yazer {yah-zare\'}; from «05826»; helpful; Jaazer or Jazer, a place East of the Jordan:--Jaazer, Jazer.', 'Jazer or Jaazer = \"helped\"<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>a Levitical city east of the Jordan, in Gilead in the territory of Gad, formerly an Amorite city; site uncertain</OL>'),
