(4108, '$lhm', 'from (01980)', 'mahlek', 'TWOT - 498d', 'mah-lake\'', 'Noun Masculine', 'from «01980»; a walking (plural collectively), i.e. access:--place to walk.', '<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>(Hiphil) walk, journey, going, place to walk<OL TYPE=\"a\"><LI>walk<LI>journey<LI>goings, free access</OL></OL>'),
