(4111, 'lallhm', 'from (04110) and (0410)', 'Mahalal\'el', 'None', 'mah-hal-al-ale\'', 'Proper Name Masculine', 'from «04110» and «0410»; praise of God; Mahalalel, the name of an antediluvian patriarch and of an Israelite:--Mahalaleel.', 'Mahalaleel = \"praise of God\"<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>son of Cainan and the 4th in descent from Adam in the line of Seth<LI>a descendant of Perez, the son of Judah</OL>'),
