(4302, '[ttm', 'from (05193)', 'matta`', 'TWOT - 1354c', 'mat-taw\'', 'Noun Masculine', 'from «05193»; something planted, i.e. the place (a garden or vineyard), or the thing (a plant, figuratively or men); by implication, the act, planting:--plant(-ation, -ing).', '<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>place or act of planting, planting, plantation<OL TYPE=\"a\"><LI>planting place<LI>act of planting<LI>plantation</OL></OL>'),
