(4313, '!wqryyh ym', 'from (04325) and (03420) with the art. interposed', 'Mey', 'None', '', 'Proper Name Location', 'from «04325» and «03420» with the art. interposed; water of the yellowness; Me-haj-Jarkon, a place in Palestine:--Me-jarkon.', 'Me-jarkon = \"waters of yellowness\"<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>a town in Dan near Joppa</OL>'),
