(6244, 'XX[', 'a primitive root', '`ashesh', 'TWOT - 1715', 'aw-shaysh\'', 'Verb', 'a primitive root; probably to shrink, i.e. fail:--be consumed.', '<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>(Qal) to waste away, fail</OL>'),
(6245, 'tX[', 'a primitive root', '`ashath', 'TWOT - 1716,1717', 'aw-shath\'', 'Verb', 'a primitive root; probably to be sleek, i.e. glossy; hence (through the idea of polishing) to excogitate (as if forming in the mind):--shine, think.', '<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>(Qal) to be smooth, be shiny, gleam<LI>(Hithpael) to think</OL>'),
