(6359, 'rytp', 'from (06362)', 'patiyr', 'TWOT - 1764', 'paw-teer\'', 'Adjective', 'from «06362»; open, i.e. unoccupied:--free.', '<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>unoccupied, free to work</OL>'),
