(6372, 'oxnyp', 'apparently from (06310) and a variation of (05175)', 'Piynchac', 'None', 'pee-nekh-aws\'', 'Proper Name Masculine', 'apparently from «06310» and a variation of «05175»; mouth of a serpent; Pinechas, the name of three Israelites:--Phinehas.', 'Phinehas = \"mouth of brass\"<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>son of Eleazar and grandson of Aaron; his zealousness for the Lord averted a plague on Israel and gained him the promise of the Lord of an everlasting priesthood in his family<LI>a priest and the son of the priest Eli<LI>the father of a helper of Ezra</OL>'),
(6373, '!nyp', 'probably the same as (06325)', 'piynon', 'None', 'pee-none\'', 'Proper Name Masculine', 'probably the same as «06325»; Pinon, an Idumaean:--Pinon.', 'Pinon = \"darkness\"<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>one of the chiefs of Edom</OL>'),
