(6375, 'qyp', 'from (06329)', 'piyq', 'TWOT - 1747b', 'peek', 'Noun Masculine', 'from «06329»; a tottering:--smite together.', '<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>tottering, staggering, stagger, stumble</OL>'),
