(6377, '!wtyp', 'probably from the same as (06596)', 'Piythown', 'None', 'pee-thone\'', 'Proper Name Masculine', 'probably from the same as «06596»; expansive; Pithon, an Israelite:--Pithon.', 'Pithon = \"harmless\"<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>son of Micah, grandson of Mephibosheth, descendant of Saul</OL>'),
