(6383, 'yalp', 'from (06381)', 'pil\'iy', 'TWOT - 1768b', 'pil-ee\'', 'Adjective', 'or «0paliy1» {paw-lee\'}; from «06381»; remarkable:--secret, wonderful.', '<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>wonderful, incomprehensible, extraordinary</OL>'),
