(6395, 'hlp', 'a primitive root', 'palah', 'TWOT - 1772', 'paw-law\'', 'Verb', 'a primitive root; to distinguish (literally or figuratively):--put a difference, show marvellous, separate, set apart, sever, make wonderfully.', '<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>to be distinct, marked out, be separated, be distinguished<OL TYPE=\"a\"><LI>(Niphal)<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>to be distinct, be separated, be distinguished<LI>to be wonderful</OL><LI>(Hiphil) to make separate, set apart</OL></OL>'),
