(6398, 'xlp', 'a primitive root', 'palach', 'TWOT - 1773', 'paw-lakh\'', 'Verb', 'a primitive root; to slice, i.e. break open or pierce:--bring forth, cleave, cut, shred, strike through.', '<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>to cleave, slice<OL TYPE=\"a\"><LI>(Qal) to cleave, plow<LI>(Piel)<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>to cleave open or through<LI>to cause to cleave open<LI>to slice, pierce</OL></OL></OL>'),
