(6419, 'llp', 'a primitive root', 'palal', 'TWOT - 1776', 'paw-lal\'', 'Verb', 'a primitive root; to judge (officially or mentally); by extension, to intercede, pray:--intreat, judge(-ment), (make) pray(-er, -ing), make supplication.', '<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>to intervene, interpose, pray<OL TYPE=\"a\"><LI>(Piel) to mediate, judge<LI>(Hithpael)<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>to intercede<LI>to pray</OL></OL></OL>'),
