(6435, '!p', 'from (06437)', 'pen', 'TWOT - 1780', 'pane', '', 'from «06437»; properly, removal; used only (in the construction) adverb as conjunction, lest:--(lest) (peradventure), that...not.', 'conj<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>lest, not, beware lest adv<LI>lest</OL>'),
