(6522, 'yzzrp', 'for (06521)', 'Prizziy', 'None', 'per-iz-zee\'', 'Adjective', 'for «06521»; inhabitant of the open country; a Perizzite, one of the Canaanitish tribes:--Perizzite.', 'Perizzite = \"belonging to a village\"<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>a people who inhabited southern Canaan prior to the conquest</OL>'),
