(6530, '#yrp', 'from (06555)', 'priyts', 'TWOT - 1826b', 'per-eets\'', 'Noun Masculine', 'from «06555»; violent, i.e. a tyrant:--destroyer, ravenous, robber.', '<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>violent one, breaker<OL TYPE=\"a\"><LI>robber, murderer</OL></OL>'),
