(6536, 'orp', 'a primitive root', 'parac', 'TWOT - 1821', 'paw-ras\'', 'Verb', 'a primitive root; to break in pieces, i.e. (usually without violence) to split, distribute:--deal, divide, have hoofs, part, tear.', '<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>to divide, break in two<OL TYPE=\"a\"><LI>(Qal) to break, break up<LI>(Hiphil) to be divided (of hoofs)</OL></OL>'),
