(6569, 'Xrp', 'from (06567)', 'peresh', 'TWOT - 1835a', 'peh\'-resh', 'Noun Masculine', 'from «06567»; excrement (as eliminated):--dung.', '<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>faecal matter, dung, offal</OL>'),
(6570, 'Xrp', 'the same as (06569)', 'Peresh', 'None', 'peh\'-resh', 'Proper Name Masculine', 'the same as «06569»; Peresh, an Israelite:--Peresh.', 'Peresh = \"dung\"<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>son of Machir by his wife Maachah</OL>'),
(6571, 'Xrp', 'from (06567)', 'parash', 'TWOT - 1836a', 'paw-rawsh\'', 'Noun Masculine', 'from «06567»; a steed (as stretched out to a vehicle, not single nor for mounting (compare «05483»)); also (by implication) a driver (in a chariot), i.e. (collectively) cavalry:--horseman.', '<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>horse, steed, warhorse<LI>horseman</OL>'),
(6572, '!gXrp', 'of foreign origin', 'parshegen', 'TWOT - 1837', 'par-sheh\'-ghen', 'Noun Masculine', 'or pathshegen {path-sheh\'-gen}; of foreign origin; a transcript:--copy.', '<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>copy</OL>'),
