(6647, '[bc', 'a root corresponding to that of (06648)', 'tsba`', 'TWOT - 2954', 'tseb-ah\'', 'Verb', '(Aramaic) a root corresponding to that of «06648»; to dip:--wet.', '<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>to dip, wet (something)<OL TYPE=\"a\"><LI>(Pael) to wet<LI>(Ithpael) to be wet</OL></OL>'),
