(6649, '!w[bc', 'from the same as (06648)', 'Tsib`own', 'None', 'tsib-one\'', 'Proper Name Masculine', 'from the same as «06648»; variegated; Tsibon, an Idumaean:--Zibeon.', 'Zibeon = \"coloured\"<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>father of Anah, whose daughter Aholibamah married Esau<LI>son of Seir the Horite<OL TYPE=\"a\"><LI>maybe same as 1</OL></OL>'),
