(6651, 'rbc', 'a primitive root', 'tsabar', 'TWOT - 1874', 'tsaw-bar\'', 'Verb', 'a primitive root; to aggregate:--gather (together), heap (up), lay up.', '<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>(Qal) to heap up, pile up<OL TYPE=\"a\"><LI>of grain, dust, silver</OL></OL>'),
