(6863, 'rc', 'from (06887)', 'Tser', 'None', 'tsare', 'Proper Name Location', 'from «06887»; rock; Tser, a place in Palestine:--Zer.', 'Zer = \"flint\"<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>fortified town in Naphtali, probably in the area of the Sea of Galilee</OL>'),
