(6884, '@rc', 'a primitive root', 'tsaraph', 'TWOT - 1972', 'tsaw-raf\'', 'Verb', 'a primitive root; to fuse (metal), i.e. refine (literally or figuratively):--cast, (re-)fine(-er), founder, goldsmith, melt, pure, purge away, try.', '<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>to smelt, refine, test<OL TYPE=\"a\"><LI>(Qal)<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>to smelt, refine<LI>to test<LI>to test (and prove true)<LI>smelter, refiner, goldsmith (participle)</OL><LI>(Niphal) to be refined<LI>(Piel) to be a refiner<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>refiner (participle)</OL></OL></OL>'),
