(7231, 'bbr', 'a primitive root', 'rabab', 'TWOT - 2099', 'raw-bab\'', 'Verb', 'a primitive root; properly, to cast together (compare «07241»), i.e. increase, especially in number; also (as denominative from «07233») to multiply by the myriad:--increase, be many(-ifold), be more, multiply, ten thousands.', '<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>to be or become many, be or become much, be or become great<OL TYPE=\"a\"><LI>(Qal)<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>to be or become many<LI>to be or become great<LI>to be long (of journey)</OL></OL><LI>(Pual) ten thousands</OL>'),
