(7275, '~gr', 'a primitive root [compare (07263), (07321), (07551)]', 'ragam', 'TWOT - 2114', 'raw-gam\'', 'Verb', 'a primitive root (compare «07263», «07321», «07551»); to cast together (stones), i.e. to lapidate:--X certainly, stone.', '<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>to stone, slay or kill by stoning<OL TYPE=\"a\"><LI>(Qal) to stone</OL></OL>'),
