(7433, 'twmr', 'from the pl. of (07413) and (01568)', 'Ramowth', 'None', 'raw-moth\'', 'Proper Name Masculine', 'or Ramoth Giliad (2 Chronicles 22:5)  {raw-moth\' gil-awd\'}; from the plural of «07413» and «01568»; heights of Gilad; Ramoth-Gilad, a place East of the Jordan:--Ramoth-gilead, Ramoth in Gilead. See also «07216».', 'Ramoth = \"heights\" n pr m<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>an Israelite who had a foreign wife in the time of Ezra n pr loc<LI>Ramoth-gilead - a place in Gilead<OL TYPE=\"a\"><LI>site dubious</OL></OL>'),
(7434, 'hpcmmh tmr', 'from (07413) and (04707) with the article interpolated', 'Ramath', 'None', '', 'Proper Name Location', 'from «07413» and «04707» with the article interpolated; height of the watch-tower; Ramath-ham- Mitspeh, a place in Palestine:--Ramath-mizpeh.', 'Ramath-mizpeh = \"high place of the watch tower\"<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>a place in Gilead on the northern border of Gad</OL>'),
