(7699, 'dX', 'probably from (07736) (in its original sense) contracted', 'shad', 'TWOT - 2332a', 'shad', 'Noun Masculine', 'or shod {shode}; probably from «07736» (in its original sense) contracted; the breast of a woman or animal (as bulging):--breast, pap, teat.', '<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>breast, bosom, (female) breast<OL TYPE=\"a\"><LI>breast (of woman)<LI>breast (of animal)<LI>breast (of both human and animal)</OL></OL>'),
