(7711, 'hpdX', 'from (07710)', 'shdephah', 'TWOT - 2335a,2335b', 'shed-ay-faw\'', '', 'or shiddaphown {shid-daw-fone\'}; from «07710»; blight:--blasted(-ing).', 'n f<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>blighted or blasted thing, blighted, blasted n m<LI>blight (of crops)</OL>'),
