(7719, '~hX', 'the same as (07718)', 'Shoham', 'None', 'sho\'-ham', 'Proper Name Masculine', 'the same as «07718»; Shoham, an Israelite:--Shoham.', 'Shoham = \"onyx\"<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>a Merarite Levite, son of Jaaziah</OL>'),
