(7734, 'gwX', 'a primitive root', 'suwg', 'TWOT - 1469', 'soog', 'Verb', 'a primitive root; to retreat:--turn back.', '<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>to move, go, turn back, turn away<OL TYPE=\"a\"><LI>(Niphal) to turn oneself away</OL></OL>'),
