(7741, '~ytyrq hwX', 'from the same as (07740) and the dual of (07151)', 'Shaveh', 'None', '', 'Proper Name Masculine', 'from the same as «07740» and the dual of «07151»; plain of a double city; Shaveh-Kirjathajim, a place East of the Jordan:--Shaveh Kiriathaim.', 'Shaveh Kiriathaim = \"plain of the double or two city\"<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>the place attacked by Chedorlaomer</OL>'),
