(7768, '[wX', 'a primitive root', 'shava`', 'TWOT - 2348', 'shaw-vah\'', 'Verb', 'a primitive root; properly, to be free; but used only causatively and reflexively, to halloo (for help, i.e. freedom from some trouble):--cry (aloud, out), shout.', '<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>(Piel) to cry out (for help), shout</OL>'),
