(7786, 'rwX', 'a primitive root', 'suwr', 'TWOT - 2287', 'soor', 'Verb', 'a primitive root; properly, to vanquish; by implication, to rule (causatively, crown):--make princes, have power, reign. See «05493».', '<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>to be or act as prince, rule, contend, have power, prevail over<OL TYPE=\"a\"><LI>(Qal) to rule over, govern<LI>(Hiphil) to make rulers, play the prince</OL></OL>'),
