(7794, 'rwX', 'from (07788)', 'showr', 'TWOT - 2355a', 'shore', 'Noun Masculine', 'from «07788»; a bullock (as a traveller):--bull(-ock), cow, ox, wall (by mistake for «07791»).', '<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>ox, bull, a head of cattle<OL TYPE=\"a\"><LI>for plowing, for food, as sacrifice</OL></OL>'),
