(7887, 'hlyX', 'from the same as (07886)', 'Shiyloh', 'TWOT - 2376', 'shee-lo\'', 'Proper Name Location', 'or Shiloh {shee-lo\'}; or Shiylow {shee-lo\'}; or Shilow {shee-lo\'}; from the same as «07886»; Shiloh, a place in Palestine:--Shiloh.', 'Shiloh = \"place of rest\"<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>a city in Ephraim and temporary home of the Ark of the Covenant and the Tabernacle, the place where Samuel grew up</OL>'),
