(8127, '!X', 'from (08150)', 'shen', 'TWOT - 2422a', 'shane', 'Noun Feminine', 'from «08150»; a tooth (as sharp); specifically (for «08143») ivory; figuratively, a cliff:--crag, × forefront, ivory, × sharp, tooth.', '<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>tooth, ivory<OL TYPE=\"a\"><LI>tooth<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>of man, lex talionis, beast</OL><LI>tooth, tine (of fork)<LI>ivory<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>as material<LI>of commerce</OL><LI>sharp pointed rock</OL></OL>'),
