(8443, 'hp[wt', 'from (03286)', 'tow`aphah', 'TWOT - 886a', 'to-aw-faw\'', 'Noun Feminine', 'from «03286»; (only in plural collective) weariness, i.e. (by implication) toil (treasure so obtained) or speed:--plenty, strength.', '<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>eminence, lofty horns, summit<OL TYPE=\"a\"><LI>eminence (of towering horns, peaks, silver)</OL></OL>'),
