(8594, 'hbr[t', 'from (06148)', 'ta`arubah', 'TWOT - 1686d', 'tah-ar-oo-baw\'', 'Noun Feminine', 'from «06148»; suretyship, i.e. (concretely) a pledge:--+ hostage.', '<OL TYPE=\"1\"><LI>pledge, surety, hostage</OL>'),
